works.description:
The image of the brown monster in the Domo
Kun Slide Puzzle infringes on the copyright of the likeness of the Domo Kun
character, which is held by NHK Enterprises, Inc. Domo Kun is a brown
monster with a rectangular body and a saw-toothed mouth that is always
open. Domo Kun is the official mascot of NHK Enterprises.
